1. Abstract class

Abstract class ek aisi class hoti hai jiska object direct nahi banaya ja sakta,
lekin usko inherit karke uske methods ko use ya override kiya ja sakta hai.

2. Use kab karte hain?
Jab aap chahte ho ki koi base class ho jisme common structure ho.

Aur subclasses us structure ko follow karen ya override karen.

Jab aap chahte ho ki kuch methods ka sirf declaration ho, definition nahi.


Abstract class me  hm jo method likhte ha oss ke age {} use nhe krte 



// abstract class Animal {
//   void makeSound(); // abstract method (no body)

